DOC.brief_summary: This is a retrospective, multicenter chart review of medical records on the use of Macrolane for female breast enhancement. The primary objective is to evaluate the safety profile of Macrolane Volume Restoration Factor 20 and Macrolane Volume Restoration Factor 30 when used for female breast enhancement in clinical practice.
DOC.criteria: Females treated with Macrolane Volume Restoration Factor 20 and/or Volume Restoration Factor 30 for breast enhancement. Signed Informed Consent Subjects that have actively asked not to be contacted by the clinic Subjects that have participated or participates in clinical studies with Macrolane for breast enhancement
